{
  "stem": "2539.3",
  "chunk_idx": 17,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were communists.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this was in the Soviet zone.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They went to the-- to the Soviet fellow and told them they wanted the apartment.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I had to leave.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I saw her in Vienna, just now, a few months ago.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She's still there in that apartment-- Nelly-- Elly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I mentioned to you before that my father survived the war in Austria, in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When he came-- the first world war-- when he came to Poland the early '20s, he met my mother in Lublin.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because my grandfather lived in Lublin.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Originally, my grandfather was not from Lublin, but he was, during the first war-- he-- they lived in Lublin, anyway.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So my father met my mother in Lublin, fell in love with her.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they married.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And Lola was born soon after.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then, of course, I came along.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Lola was born in '22.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] It was a couple that never argued.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My father was so much in love with my mother that-- and she was just-- they never-- I've never heard an argument in the house.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Maybe that's why I didn't argue with Lola, because I've never heard people arguing-- argue in my life-- until the war, of course-- until, you know, I saw people kill each other.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I've never-- I've never-- I never known that-- I've never know that people can argue.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was such a harmonious, quiet place, wonderful place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "For instance, in Lutsk, we used to go to high school, come back home at 3 o'clock, or shortly after, a few minutes after.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We used to have dinner together and discuss everything under the sun.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There was my mother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There was my father at the head of the table.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There was me and Lola.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
